# Git Commit Helper for traceflux
# Purpose: Guide Conventional Commits 1.0.0 specification
# Usage: workflow check workflow/commit.workflow.list
# Reference: https://www.conventionalcommits.org/en/v1.0.0/

- (start) Traceflux Commit Workflow
  # Import base commit workflow from workflow-as-list
  import: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/tracer-mohist/workflow-as-list/refs/heads/main/examples/git/commit.workflow.list

- (traceflux-specific) Apply traceflux conventions
  # traceflux-specific commit conventions
  - NOTE: src/ changes use feat/fix (triggers version)
  - NOTE: scripts/ changes use chore (no version bump)
  - NOTE: tests/ changes use test

- End
